{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Server Timing",
    "url": "https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "parse a server-timing header field",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#parse-a-server-timing-header-field",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"parse-a-server-timing-header-field\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">parse a server-timing header field</dfn> given a string <var>field</var>:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>position</var> be a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string-position-variable\" id=\"ref-for-string-position-variable\">position variable</a>, initially pointing at the start of <var>field</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>name</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#collect-a-sequence-of-code-points\" id=\"ref-for-collect-a-sequence-of-code-points\">collecting a sequence of code points</a> from <var>field</var> that are not equal to U+003B (;), given <var>position</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#strip-leading-and-trailing-ascii-whitespace\" id=\"ref-for-strip-leading-and-trailing-ascii-whitespace\">Strip leading and trailing ASCII whitespace</a> from <var>name</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>name</var> is an empty string, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>metric</var> be a new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#performanceservertiming\" id=\"ref-for-performanceservertiming①\">PerformanceServerTiming</a></code> whose <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#performanceservertiming-metric-name\" id=\"ref-for-performanceservertiming-metric-name\">metric name</a> is <var>name</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>params</var> be an empty <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map\">ordered map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "While <var>position</var> is not at the end of <var>field</var>:",
          "rationale": "advance",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Advance <var>position</var> by 1.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>paramName</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#collect-a-sequence-of-code-points\" id=\"ref-for-collect-a-sequence-of-code-points①\">collecting a sequence of code points</a> from <var>field</var> that are not equal to U+003D (=), given <var>position</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#strip-leading-and-trailing-ascii-whitespace\" id=\"ref-for-strip-leading-and-trailing-ascii-whitespace①\">Strip leading and trailing ASCII whitespace</a> from <var>paramName</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>paramName</var> is an empty string or <var>params</var>[<var>paramName</var>] <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists\">exists</a>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#iteration-continue\" id=\"ref-for-iteration-continue\">continue</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Advance <var>position</var> by 1.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>paramValue</var> be an empty string.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#skip-ascii-whitespace\" id=\"ref-for-skip-ascii-whitespace\">Skip ASCII whitespace</a> within <var>field</var> given <var>position</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#code-point\" id=\"ref-for-code-point\">code point</a> at <var>position</var> within <var>field</var> is U+0022 (\"), then:",
              "rationale": "set",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>Set <var>paramValue</var> to the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#collect-an-http-quoted-string\" id=\"ref-for-collect-an-http-quoted-string\">collecting an HTTP quoted string</a> from <var>field</var> given <var>position</var> with the <i>extract-value flag</i> set.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#collect-a-sequence-of-code-points\" id=\"ref-for-collect-a-sequence-of-code-points②\">Collect a sequence of code points</a> from <var>field</var> that are not equal to U+003B (;), given <var>position</var>. The result is not used.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise:",
              "rationale": "let",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>Let <var>rawParamValue</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#collect-a-sequence-of-code-points\" id=\"ref-for-collect-a-sequence-of-code-points③\">collecting a sequence of code points</a> from <var>field</var> that are not equal to U+003B (;), given <var>position</var>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>Let <var>paramValue</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#strip-leading-and-trailing-ascii-whitespace\" id=\"ref-for-strip-leading-and-trailing-ascii-whitespace②\">stripping</a> <var>rawParamValue</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-set\" id=\"ref-for-map-set\">Set</a> <var>metric</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#performanceservertiming-params\" id=\"ref-for-performanceservertiming-params\">params</a> to <var>params</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>metric</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "The <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#dom-performanceservertiming-duration\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performanceservertiming-duration②\">duration</a></code> getter steps are to do the following:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#performanceservertiming-params\" id=\"ref-for-performanceservertiming-params①\">params</a>[<code>\"dur\"</code>] does not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists①\">exist</a>, return 0.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>dur</var> be the result of parsing <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this②\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#performanceservertiming-params\" id=\"ref-for-performanceservertiming-params②\">params</a>[<code>\"dur\"</code>] using the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/common-microsyntaxes.html#rules-for-parsing-floating-point-number-values\" id=\"ref-for-rules-for-parsing-floating-point-number-values\">rules for parsing floating-point number values</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>dur</var> is an error, return 0; Otherwise return <var>dur</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "PerformanceResourceTiming/serverTiming",
      "href": "https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#dom-performanceresourcetiming-servertiming",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled idl-code has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"PerformanceResourceTiming\" data-dfn-type=\"attribute\" data-export=\"\" id=\"dom-performanceresourcetiming-servertiming\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><code>serverTiming</code></dfn> getter steps are the following:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>entries</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list\" id=\"ref-for-list\">list</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate\">For each</a> <var>field</var> in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this④\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/resource-timing/#dfn-timing-info\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-timing-info\">timing info</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#fetch-timing-info-server-timing-headers\" id=\"ref-for-fetch-timing-info-server-timing-headers\">server-timing headers</a>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>metric</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/server-timing/#parse-a-server-timing-header-field\" id=\"ref-for-parse-a-server-timing-header-field\">parsing</a> <var>field</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>metric</var> is not null, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-append\" id=\"ref-for-list-append\">append</a> <var>metric</var> to <var>entries</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>entries</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}